Ekí akbeyatshak jiaga, Duwejañki ni ezua múldigaba nuxaki izhakuaká zhikzukuaxaldiamak yokuazhá. Ekí tuatshakna sáñkaldaja “¡sakí nak shi ishkualdazhá gu!” jañguiñgaba na gua.
Duwe Jesú shuigakue agatsé axeyatene<TS3>(<a href="b41.15.6-20">Mlk 15.6-20</a>; <a href="b42.23.13-25">Lk 23.13-25</a>; <a href="b43.18.38–19.16">Jñ 18.38–19.16</a>)Guatshak nauwisanákueki Jateja san kagixa zhinik kakzʉxaitshanéñ ldiuwañ be izhgisekui kajuizhaldegauxa Alduma zalda sáñkaldaja mielde paldesu nukaki kakibesakue ishkakuxaldiake kakibesamakga kakibesixa.
