Aldéñga ezua kamakue zʉnekualdal zʉñgakagatukaki,Eñki nauwibama sáñkalda Dabí, axazauñka nanetshi atukuaga<RF q=+><a href="b19.132.17">Sal 132.17</a> ni zʉñgakagatók.
