Amak kabexane nalgué jiaga, ai siañki Saldiñga netshi Sáñkaldajañga aldéñ guaklde uldeñka kagakagatshak kalse kagakpeshi, kakzʉxaitshiñgueniki
ekí kakbeyá: “Juwí Jate axazakuageñka mineyaldí. Exa akté noshi, Jateja Asukuák zhinik abisajañ mimakukshi izhoshiñga mimezhokshaka<RF q=+><a href="b43.11.25">Jñ 11.25</a>; <a href="b43.14.6">14.6</a>; <a href="b45.6.4">Alm 6.4</a> shalda auxaga exa zhekuekuek miyakbeyaldí.”
