Mieldeke Duwe Jesú shalda sha zʉnakualdiák, Jateja ekíga kakiyushakue akshishagába, janshizhe kaxatshaldiamak niñkauwañki akshishakue.<RF q=+><a href="b40.5.44">Mt 5.44</a>; <a href="b42.6.28">Lk 6.28</a>
